snippet.title: Live Coding: Android Port Scanner
snippet.description:
Let's tackle a relatively simple project tonight: a port scanner app for Android. We'll focus on building a minimal but useful port scanner for Android devices.

GitHub: https://www.github.com/DevDungeon
Support the stream: https://streamlabs.com/devdungeon
Join Discord: https://discord.gg/JWsSHJC
Get $100 credit for signing up to Digital Ocean: https://m.do.co/c/5ccd98162d85
